@ScottCarnahan maybe you already have more material? In that case, would you mind opening another PR that has all the material? That helps with reviewing.

For the current PR, I would suggest keeping the first 3 defs `pairing`, `coxeterWeight`, and `IsOrthogonal`, and writing a few API lemmas about them like `coxeterWeight_swap` and `IsOrthogonal_comm` and `IsOrthogonal.symm`.

I guess the other definitions will come with more serious API.
